        <p>We tested 10 of the most-recommended AI SEO platforms across content quality, optimization accuracy, publishing depth, and pricing. Tests ran on real sites in HVAC, dental, SaaS, and e-commerce niches over a 90-day window. Here is the honest ranking — and why most "AI SEO" buyers end up paying twice.</p>

