          <li><strong>Test sites</strong> — 4 real sites in HVAC, dental, SaaS, and e-commerce, DA 18–34.</li>
          <li><strong>Scope</strong> — 6 articles per platform, identical SERP targets, fresh accounts.</li>
          <li><strong>Measurement</strong> — output quality (editor review), optimization score (Surfer/Clearscope grade), and 90-day rank movement.</li>
          <li><strong>Total spend</strong> — $6,420 across 10 subscriptions, 90-day window.</li>
        </ul>

